011 to discuss the future funding for community pharmacy. A “Community Pharmacy Future project” was initiated as a result with a vision of demonstrating the </span><span style="color:#0d0d0d; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">benefits pharmacy can offer, with an approach of reducing primary care admissions and delivering benefits for all parties. The project group looked at the delivery of services that address key objectives for Governments three areas of focus including:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="color:#0d0d0d; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="color:#0d0d0d; font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="color:#0d0d0d; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Medicine optimisation</span></li><li style="color:#0d0d0d; font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="color:#0d0d0d; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Public Health</span></li><li style="color:#0d0d0d; font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="color:#0d0d0d; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Self care</span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="color:#0d0d0d; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="color:#0d0d0d; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">2.2 </span><span style="color:#0d0d0d; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Two services were developed to demonstrate pharmacies ability to manage long term conditions. The services were developed and a pi</span><span style="color:#0d0d0d; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">lot launched in September 2012 </span><span style